{
  "stem": "23832.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Your dog has the right to live, and I don't have the right to live.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now, my sister had this boyfriend that I told you, and he had a friend-- a colleague, a doctor, a German, Dr.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "George Tille.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this doctor had [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] a sister, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and they're like friends.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he knew of that man who would bring me the papers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So one day at 3:00, I was supposed to be in the woods.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Regretfully, that I don't have the papers to show you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I have it in the house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when you move from here to this other address, it's all in the book.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Goes to the police.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So you cannot hide.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So when they-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was there, and I didn't have any of those slips, those things that shows that I came out of the ghetto, that I am registered, because I wasn't.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was this woman-- this woman that she-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when I was with this little baby, Anthony, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] she had one cow.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She had many.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This particular cow, that milks, do not mix with all the milks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That milk is for Anthony's drink.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she was boiling that milk in a little pot, and she put that pot-- and I had nothing to do with it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In came the cat and drank that milk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she came and grabbed me like this and said, now, you better go because when my husband comes, he'll kill you.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she grabbed a stick to hit me.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
